[
    {
        "text": "One year and 13 days ago, I lost my husband Dave.",
        "startTime": 1229,
        "endTime": 5947,
        "slowStartTime": 1993,
        "slowEndTime": 9145
    },
    {
        "text": "One day, my friend Adam Grant, a psychologist,...",
        "startTime": 8022,
        "endTime": 10881,
        "slowStartTime": 12183,
        "slowEndTime": 16547
    },
    {
        "text": "...suggested that I think about how much worse things could be.",
        "startTime": 11181,
        "endTime": 14599,
        "slowStartTime": 16922,
        "slowEndTime": 22123
    },
    {
        "text": "This was completely counterintuitive to me.",
        "startTime": 15695,
        "endTime": 17839,
        "slowStartTime": 23693,
        "slowEndTime": 26984
    },
    {
        "text": "I would've thought that getting through something like death...",
        "startTime": 18284,
        "endTime": 20835,
        "slowStartTime": 27576,
        "slowEndTime": 31477
    },
    {
        "text": "...was about finding every positive thought I could.",
        "startTime": 21177,
        "endTime": 24223,
        "slowStartTime": 31915,
        "slowEndTime": 36560
    },
    {
        "text": "\"Worse?\" I said to him.",
        "startTime": 25039,
        "endTime": 26561,
        "slowStartTime": 37709,
        "slowEndTime": 40066
    },
    {
        "text": "\"Are you crazy? How could things be worse?\"",
        "startTime": 26846,
        "endTime": 30326,
        "slowStartTime": 40419,
        "slowEndTime": 45714
    },
    {
        "text": "He looked at me and said,...",
        "startTime": 32196,
        "endTime": 34480,
        "slowStartTime": 48444,
        "slowEndTime": 51945
    },
    {
        "text": "\"Dave could've had that same cardiac arrhythmia driving your children.\"",
        "startTime": 35125,
        "endTime": 39657,
        "slowStartTime": 52838,
        "slowEndTime": 59711
    },
    {
        "text": "The minute he said it, I felt overwhelming gratitude that my children were alive...",
        "startTime": 45602,
        "endTime": 52673,
        "slowStartTime": 68553,
        "slowEndTime": 79234
    },
    {
        "text": "...and that gratitude overtook some of the grief.",
        "startTime": 53114,
        "endTime": 57274,
        "slowStartTime": 79821,
        "slowEndTime": 86136
    },
    {
        "text": "My hope for you is that you can find that gratitude,...",
        "startTime": 58382,
        "endTime": 61861,
        "slowStartTime": 87723,
        "slowEndTime": 93017
    },
    {
        "text": "...not just on the easy days like today,...",
        "startTime": 62323,
        "endTime": 65089,
        "slowStartTime": 93634,
        "slowEndTime": 97859
    },
    {
        "text": "...but on the hard days when you will need it.",
        "startTime": 65542,
        "endTime": 68340,
        "slowStartTime": 98463,
        "slowEndTime": 102735
    },
    {
        "text": "You are not born with a fixed amount of resilience.",
        "startTime": 69750,
        "endTime": 72239,
        "slowStartTime": 104775,
        "slowEndTime": 108583
    },
    {
        "text": "It's a muscle.",
        "startTime": 72587,
        "endTime": 73714,
        "slowStartTime": 109031,
        "slowEndTime": 110796
    },
    {
        "text": "You can build it up and then draw on it when you need it.",
        "startTime": 74091,
        "endTime": 77880,
        "slowStartTime": 111286,
        "slowEndTime": 117045
    },
    {
        "text": "And in that process, you figure out who you really are,...",
        "startTime": 78575,
        "endTime": 82983,
        "slowStartTime": 118012,
        "slowEndTime": 124699
    },
    {
        "text": "...and you just might become the very best version of yourself.",
        "startTime": 83471,
        "endTime": 90232,
        "slowStartTime": 125356,
        "slowEndTime": 135573
    }
]